    {
      "title": "HuggingFace 中的多选题问答-CSDN博客",
      "link": "https://blog.csdn.net/wizardforcel/article/details/157760208",
      "snippet": "原文:towardsdatascience.com/multichoice-question-answering-in-huggingface-96f61eb88d18 https://github.com/OpenDocCN/towardsdatascience-blog-zh-2024/raw/master/docs/img/b9585d4972759e558c2c2be9be0478a1.png 图片来自 unsplash.com 自然语言处理技术在问答(QA)任务上展现出巨大的能力｡",
